# 🎤 2) CARTESIA / VOICE MAPPING LAYER

This is where emotion graph becomes **voice behavior**.

```ts id="vx_voice_1"
export function mapEmotionToVoice(audioState: any) {
  const { intensity, speechStyle, musicPresence } = audioState;

  return {
    rate: 1.0 + intensity * 0.2,
    pitch: 1.0 - intensity * 0.1,
    energy: intensity,
    style: speechStyle,
    backgroundMix: musicPresence,
  };
}
```

